{"tid":2054532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《共同社》報道日本拒絕加入歐美國家批評港區國安法聯合聲明","createTime":"2020-06-07T08:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T12:06:10.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfe1e53e1444d2912095839eebeec47f8a106e0","tid":2054532,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530678-20200607.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530678-20200607.htm&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=9a8c5234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530678-20200607.htm&h=faea13e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530678-20200607.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n《共同社》報道，日本政府拒絕加入美英等國家，嚴厲批評中國在香港制訂國安法的聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，英美、澳洲和加拿大就港區國安法發表聯合聲明前，曾經暗中詢問日本，但日方拒絕參加。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述多名日本相關人士透露，日方希望與中國改善關係，中國國家主席習近平因為新型肺炎疫情推遲對日本進行國賓訪問，有意見認為，日方是為了避免過度刺激中國。<br />\n<br />\n歐美各國就香港問題與中國對立加深，日本的決定可能導致與歐美各國之間產生裂痕。<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官菅義偉上月底曾對香港建立國安法稱深表憂慮。"},{"pid":"61e1f839763395f8122c1141dd8c489916ac2a13","tid":2054532,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb37e5ef93b612fffe26bd5c0db1835998643c54","tid":2054532,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"無人諗到日本軍國主義果陣果種霸氣<br />\n大東亞共榮圈<br />\n亞洲leader<br />\n係中國想殺邊個殺邊個 想姦邊個姦邊個<br />\n到宜家居然要睇番中國面色做人<br />\n可唔可以比番d火黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861436b4a96f4dd044e34eca789095cf8d350816","tid":2054532,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"扶桑省當然要緊跟中央政府"},{"pid":"15cba3537c48613b1b110b05edcfa11a116c8dad","tid":2054532,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB